meanings: 대화 도중 Can you keep a secret?
대화 도중 You can keep a secret, can't you?
(재산·목숨·나라 등을) guard, (방어하다) defend, protect, (보호하다) look after, take care of
(약속·법·질서 등을) keep, obey, follow, observe, stick[adhere] to, uphold

meanings.meaning: a climb-down from an untenable position
